{"service_name": "Business Continuity Exercises", "service_id": "6533063429324800", "company_name": "Evolve Secure Solutions Limited", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Evolve Secure Solutions Limited\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Business Continuity Exercises\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Our specialist G-Cloud service offering includes exercising to rehearse the roles of team members and to test the plans for continuity of critical business functions including all cloud aspects. This enables prompt recovery to \u2018business as usual\u2019 and ensures continuity of cloud and other services.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Development includes comprehensive background briefs for teams prior to events\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Full report highlights issues arising and recommended actions for improvement\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Scenario led exercises for rehearsing the teams\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Single team or several teams dependent on the scale\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Full simulation under conditions that simulate a crisis event\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Access to all specialist skills with real time crisis experience\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Increased levels of resilience for information, systems and applications\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Accuracy of recovery time objectives, and recovery point objectives\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Availability of information, data and applications for processes and activities\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Compliance benchmarked with ISO 22301\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Integration with existing policy and decision making processes\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Low cost, high value approach tailored to our customer\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Independent and impartial advice in your best interest\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Contingency and continuity of service assured by Evolve team approach\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     VFM services tailored to customer business imperatives and timescales\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Quality of Service assured by ISO9001, ISO27001, ISO14001, CLAS certifications\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3800 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92536/6533063429324800-pricing-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92536/6533063429324800-sfia-rate-card.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92536/6533063429324800-service-definition-document.pdf\">